title: McKenna, Washington
text:
McKenna is an <a href="unincorporated%20area">unincorporated community</a> in <a href="Pierce%20County%2C%20Washington">Pierce County</a>, <a href="Washington%20%28state%29">Washington</a>, United States, located on <a href="Washington%20State%20Route%20507">State Route 507</a> and the <a href="Nisqually%20River">Nisqually River</a>, east of <a href="Yelm%2C%20Washington">Yelm</a>.
Founded around 1908, McKenna is a former timber <a href="company%20town">company town</a>.
